subSubSection.paragraph:
Caryocolum fibigerium

in its current taxonomic sense is confirmed from the Iberian Peninsula (Spain) and southern parts of France (
Huemer and Karsholt 2010
), whereas other published records from Morocco (
Huemer 1988
), Portugal (
Corley 2015
), and northern Italy (
Karsholt and Huemer 1995
) require re-examination including DNA barcode analysis.
